Pleistocene,geological,-61050,-61050,data/google-drive-pdfs/Alor_Pleistocene_HumanSkull.pdf,2,"ntaining Homo ﬂoresiensis in Flores (Sutikna et al., 2016, 2018), substantive dating of the cave context of Homo sapiens fossil material in Sumatra at 73,000 e63,000 BP (Westaway et al., 2017 ), and new sites with human Pleistocene deposits in several Wallacean islands have sparked renewed in- terest in this region. * Corresponding author. E-mail address: soﬁa.samper@anu.edu.au (S.C. Samper Carro). Contents lists available at ScienceDirect Journal"
