Prehistoric,archaeological,,,data/google-drive-pdfs/Animal motifs on rock art in Papua and West Papua.pdf,38,"ancestral spirits. House lizards are animals which tend to live in more elevated places, often in houses, whereas most other lizards live under or on the ground. In this regard, house lizards and lizards are related to prehistoric religious concepts which acknowledge an Upper World and an Underworld. The house lizard motif is considered a reflection of the Upper World, while lizards (and snakes) represent the Underworld (Permana 2019: 30). Anothe"
