Holocene,geological,,,"data/google-drive-pdfs/Asian Paleoanthropology From Africa to China and Beyond (Christopher J. Norton, David R. Braun (auth.) etc.) (z-lib.org).pdf",110,"ang et al. 2007). Warm and humid adapted plant and animal taxa retreated back south of the Qinling Mountain Range. Increase in Gramineae in the north indicates a cooler, more open environment (Whyte 1984). 5. During the Holocene the climate stabilized to within 1–3°C of the present day. There was a warming trend dur- ing the Early-Middle Holocene that coincides, and may be a direct, or indirect, cause for the advent of plant and animal domestic"
